---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/global/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/global/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — Family Healthcare"
  description="Terms of Service for Family Healthcare — the private family health management app."
  canonicalUrl="https://thestackmint.com/terms"
>
  <Header brand="familyhealth" backLink="/familyhealth" />

  <main>
    <section style="padding:64px 0 84px">
      <div class="legal">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Effective: June 2026</p>
        <h2>1. Acceptance</h2>
        <p>By using Family Healthcare, you agree to these Terms, forming a binding agreement with thestackmint, India.</p>
        <h2>2. Account registration</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide accurate information; keep credentials secure</li>
          <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorised access</li>
          <li>Must be 18+ to create an account</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>3. Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>Do not upload malware, reverse-engineer the app, circumvent security, impersonate others, scrape data, or harm infrastructure.</p>
        <h2>4. Health disclaimer</h2>
        <div class="notice">
          <strong>Not medical advice.</strong> Family Healthcare is a personal health record tool, not a medical device or healthcare provider.
          Always consult a qualified healthcare professional before any health or medication decision.
        </div>
        <h2>5. Subscription &amp; billing</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Free, Premium (₹199/mo), Family Pro (₹499/mo) — billed monthly in INR</li>
          <li>Upgrade/downgrade anytime from the app; downgrading preserves existing data in read-only mode</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>6. Your data</h2>
        <p>You own all health data you enter. You can export and permanently delete it at any time from Privacy Settings.</p>
        <h2>7. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>The App, design, and branding are the exclusive property of thestackmint.</p>
        <h2>8. Termination</h2>
        <p>We may suspend accounts violating these Terms. You may delete your account at any time; data is deleted within 30 days.</p>
        <h2>9. Liability</h2>
        <p>The App is provided "as is". Our total liability shall not exceed the greater of ₹5,000 or amounts paid in the prior 12 months.</p>
        <h2>10. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>You agree to indemnify thestackmint from claims arising from your use of the App or violation of these Terms.</p>
        <h2>11. Governing law</h2>
        <p>Governed by the laws of <strong>India</strong>. Disputes subject to Indian courts.</p>
        <h2>12. Changes</h2>
        <p>Material changes notified via in-app notice at least <strong>7 days</strong> before taking effect.</p>
        <h2>13. Contact</h2>
        <p><strong>thestackmint</strong> · <a href="mailto:familyhealth@thestackmint.com">familyhealth@thestackmint.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer brand="familyhealth" />
</BaseLayout>
